snippet.title: Demonetisation: December 15, Last Day to Use Old Rs 500 Notes

localized.description:
Demonetisation: December 15 is last day to use old Rs 500 notes. Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
